</math></stem>
</p>
<p id="_43bed9c4-d995-4c13-ac1f-4008d469ad1a">with a relative uncertainty of <stem type="MathML"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mn>1.9</mn><mo>&#215;</mo><msup><mrow><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow><mrow><mo>&#8722;</mo><mn>15</mn></mrow></mrow></msup></math></stem>.</p>
